      <a href="/about/">About me</a>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-card reveal">
      <span class="feature-number">03</span>
      <h2>Publications</h2>
      <p>
        My publication record includes research in IEEE Access, CAAI Transactions on Intelligence Technology,
        EURASIP Journal, and international conference proceedings.
      </p>
      <a href="/publications/">View publications</a>
